    <meta name="keywords" content="Gaudi 3, AI, IBM Cloud, software models, Nvidia H100, Nvidia H200 inferencing, LLMs, accelerators, Cloud, on-prem, Signal 65, OAM"/>
    <meta name="description" content="An overview of the Signal65 performance benchmarking of the Intel® Gaudi® 3 AI accelerator, highlighting performance against NVIDIA&#39;s H100 and H200 GPUs. Conducted by Signal65, the testing reveals that Gaudi 3 offers superior price-to-performance ratios, particularly in on-premises and IBM Cloud environments. The Intel® Gaudi® 3 AI accelerator demonstrates higher throughput and cost efficiency, especially for large AI workloads, making it a compelling choice for enterprises seeking scalable and economical AI solutions. This is a companion to the Signal65 white papers:

Intel® Gaudi® 3 AI Accelerator at Scale on IBM Cloud — White Paper
https://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/content-details/853099/content-details.html

Decentralizing Generative AI (GenAI) Inference On Device — White Paper
https://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/content-details/850477/content-details.html"/>
    <meta name="robots" content="follow,index,noarchive"/>

