            <!-- [START] ------------------ Metadata information ------------------ -->
            <div class="cd-page-overview-metadata">
                <div class="cd-page-overview-metadata__details cd-page-overview-metadata-description">
                    <h2 class="cd-page-overview-metadata_description__label">Description</h2>
                    <p class="cd-page-overview-metadata_description__content">
                        <p>An overview of the Signal65 performance benchmarking of the Intel® Gaudi® 3 AI accelerator, highlighting performance against NVIDIA's H100 and H200 GPUs. Conducted by Signal65, the testing reveals that Gaudi 3 offers superior price-to-performance ratios, particularly in on-premises and IBM Cloud environments. The Intel® Gaudi® 3 AI accelerator demonstrates higher throughput and cost efficiency, especially for large AI workloads, making it a compelling choice for enterprises seeking scalable and economical AI solutions. This is a companion to the Signal65 white papers:</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/content-details/853099/content-details.html" target="_blank">Intel® Gaudi® 3 AI Accelerator at Scale on IBM Cloud — White Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/content-details/850477/content-details.html" target="_blank">Decentralizing Generative AI (GenAI) Inference On Device — White Paper</a></li></ul>
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="cd-page-overview-metadata__details cd-page-overview-metadata-instructions" id="instructions_metadata">
                    <h2 class="cd-page-overview-metadata_Instructions__label">Usage instructions</h2>
                    <p class="cd-page-overview-metadata_instructions__content" id="instructions_metadata_content"></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- [END] ------------------ Metadata information ------------------ -->
            <div id='cd-page-overview-preview-modal'>
            </div>
        </div>
    


